title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 24 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 24 2022
description:
Clay and Buck speculate about DOJ "big announcement" scheduled for 1:30PM ET. Blue state Dems attempt last-minute flip-flop on crime. Buck asks, "Did Kathy Hochul just realize she needs to keep her job?" Ted Cruz crushes The View hosts, triggers their insane audience. Clay says, "Ted Cruz was an Ivy League debate champion, so he filleted the women of The View." Joe Biden once again flubs a question on his age, cognitive difficulties, comes out in favor of genital mutilation for children in interview with transgender TikTok influencer. Can't-miss clips from Ted Cruz on The View.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
